ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectRainy River First Nations (Ontario) ** Creation **
PrecisOrder setting apart 278.977 hectares (689.367 acres), more or less, of land including mines and minerals, for the use and benefit of the Rainy River First Nations, as a new reserve identified as RAINY RIVER FIRST NATIONS NO.1, located in the districts of Kenora and Rainy River at approximately 30 kilometres from Nestor Falls, in Ontario.
